WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.080 --> 00:00:11.386
Hi, my name is Brandon, and I have had an experience with the Lord that he keeps telling me I need to tell people about.

00:00:11.760 --> 00:00:27.188
I've never really talked in front of a camera before like this, but he wanted me to document it and tell everybody what happened and what kind of experience I had with him.

00:00:27.554 --> 00:00:40.194
This experience lasted all night long, and I'm just asking the Holy Spirit right now to help me communicate everything that I saw.

00:00:41.093 --> 00:00:47.783
It's really important because Jesus Christ is coming, and he told me he's coming face to face.

00:00:49.702 --> 00:00:59.421
This experience happened on July 6th, 2014, and I've held it all these years.

00:00:59.421 --> 00:01:06.640
I wrote it down on paper and released it to some people on Facebook and to some church friends and family.

00:01:09.530 --> 00:01:13.588
Some people received it and some people didn't.

00:01:14.617 --> 00:01:19.244
I'm just a deliverer of the message that he gave me.

00:01:19.244 --> 00:01:32.540
I'm not here to argue about theology or try to convince anybody of my experience.

00:01:33.140 --> 00:01:42.506
I'm going to tell you exactly what happened, exactly how it happened, from the beginning to the end.

00:01:43.544 --> 00:01:51.240
I don't know if you're a mid-tribulation, post-tribulation, or pre-tribulation believer.

00:01:55.827 --> 00:02:06.159
Like I said, I'm not here to argue or try to get you to say anything in the comments about what I saw or what I experienced.

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:12.200
I'm just telling you what I saw and we'll go from there.

00:02:13.088 --> 00:02:20.571
It all started out while I was asleep; I went to bed a normal night, nothing different.

00:02:20.571 --> 00:02:27.984
I went to sleep and in the middle of my sleep, all of a sudden, I don't know if I was in my body or out of my body.

00:02:29.856 --> 00:02:42.879
I don't know how it happened; all I know is all of a sudden I was standing with Jesus, and he was on my right hand the whole time in this experience.

00:02:42.879 --> 00:02:49.260
He grabbed a hold of my hand and I'll go from there.

00:02:49.792 --> 00:02:58.024
The first scene, per se, of what I saw was Jesus standing on my right hand.

00:02:58.024 --> 00:03:01.716
He had a hold of my hand and we were in a town.

00:03:01.716 --> 00:03:09.120
I don't know what town we were in, but I know that there was a big white building over to the side.

00:03:10.719 --> 00:03:18.530
I was looking up at this big white building and at the sky, and the sky was alive.

00:03:18.530 --> 00:03:27.539
It was like it was moving; it was full of lightning and very spooky looking.

00:03:28.699 --> 00:03:37.813
I looked out over the horizon and there was this lady running towards me, and she started screaming.

00:03:37.813 --> 00:03:41.680
They were all screaming in terror; they were all freaking out.

00:03:41.680 --> 00:03:44.168
It was incredible.

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:48.720
They were saying, "They're gone.

00:03:48.720 --> 00:03:49.154
They're gone.

00:03:50.023 --> 00:03:51.970
" I said, "Who's gone?

00:03:52.180 --> 00:03:54.280
" I told this lady, "Who's gone?

00:03:54.280 --> 00:03:57.297
" and she said, "Did you not see?

00:03:57.546 --> 00:03:59.460
" I said, "Did I not see what, ma'am?

00:03:59.880 --> 00:04:02.069
What are you talking about?

00:04:02.339 --> 00:04:04.630
" At this time, she could see me.

00:04:04.630 --> 00:04:12.427
Now, not every time in this experience were people able to see me.

00:04:12.738 --> 00:04:19.172
In this instance, she could not see Jesus, but she could see me.

00:04:19.519 --> 00:04:21.165
She said, "The aliens?

00:04:21.988 --> 00:04:25.647
The aliens came and got the Christians.

00:04:26.213 --> 00:04:28.479
" I said, "The aliens?

00:04:28.479 --> 00:04:30.808
" She said, "Yes, they all disappeared.

00:04:30.808 --> 00:04:32.512
They went up.

00:04:34.340 --> 00:04:37.280
" At that moment, she just ran off.

00:04:37.280 --> 00:04:40.360
She was frantic, screaming in terror.

00:04:42.137 --> 00:04:43.884
She ran as fast as she could, panicking.

00:04:44.289 --> 00:04:47.712
I looked out over the horizon of the city.

00:04:47.712 --> 00:04:53.340
I was up on a hill at this time and I could see everything on fire.

00:04:53.340 --> 00:04:58.582
Everything was on fire—the cars, the houses, the buildings.

00:04:59.908 --> 00:05:07.600
It was like chaos beyond anything you could ever comprehend was happening at this time.

00:05:07.970 --> 00:05:09.820
You could smell the smoke.

00:05:10.560 --> 00:05:14.432
People were looting; they were stealing out of cars and buildings.

00:05:14.432 --> 00:05:20.133
They were trashing the city where I was.

00:05:21.040 --> 00:05:23.320
Jesus didn't say anything.

00:05:24.240 --> 00:05:29.973
In fact, he never spoke; I could perceive his thoughts when he was touching my hand.

00:05:29.973 --> 00:05:34.999
I knew what he was thinking, but he never said anything out of his mouth.

00:05:34.999 --> 00:05:41.919
He could understand what I was thinking, but I never said anything to him.

00:05:41.919 --> 00:05:47.440
I was just looking across the city, thinking, "Oh my gosh, what is going on?

00:05:47.1000 --> 00:05:51.359
" All of a sudden, we translated.

00:05:51.359 --> 00:05:54.120
We left that spot and went to another spot.

00:05:56.263 --> 00:06:01.792
He grabbed my hand—we were still holding hands—but it was like we just disappeared and came to another time.

00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:12.524
In this time frame, I was looking over Europe.

00:06:12.524 --> 00:06:17.867
I knew I was looking over Europe because I was standing back, like I was watching a movie.

00:06:17.867 --> 00:06:19.467
It was very strange.

00:06:19.733 --> 00:06:27.693
I was looking out over Europe and I saw this man in Berlin.

00:06:28.222 --> 00:06:31.885
All the world leaders were behind a table.

00:06:31.885 --> 00:06:34.026
It was a round table in Berlin.

00:06:34.026 --> 00:06:37.227
It looked like a big "" office.

00:06:38.009 --> 00:06:41.680
It was a brown table, and there were chairs all around it.

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:57.439
All of these world leaders were behind this big table, and this man—I didn't know who he was at the time, but I'll tell you later—and all of the people were asking him for help.

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:08.640
They were asking him for a solution to all the rioting and the craziness that was going on.

00:07:09.200 --> 00:07:13.400
He was instructing them on what to do.

00:07:13.400 --> 00:07:21.300
He had all the wisdom and was very powerful in demeanor, the way he carried himself.

00:07:21.300 --> 00:07:28.089
He was wearing a gray suit, and he was a Middle Eastern man.

00:07:29.795 --> 00:07:47.703
All of a sudden, that scene was over, but the Lord at that time spoke to me about a scripture and showed me how everyone would give over their kingdoms to him within one hour.

00:07:47.703 --> 00:07:58.453
As I said, I'm not a Bible scholar or a theology major; I'm just a guy who loves Jesus and seeks Him with all my heart, and I had this experience with Him.

00:08:05.916 --> 00:08:07.392
The next scene I see is this man on TV—he's on CNN, Fox, and everywhere.

00:08:16.940 --> 00:08:26.720
He is telling all the people of the world what happened to the people who disappeared, explaining that they were rebellious, that they were taken away out of rebellion, and that they were being punished.

00:08:39.760 --> 00:08:45.460
All these people were punished—it was the Christians, and they were all being taken out.

00:08:45.790 --> 00:08:50.223
Then he explained that he was the new leader of the world.

00:08:51.167 --> 00:08:57.213
I looked out and saw how he was gradually taking power.

00:09:01.227 --> 00:09:06.792
I want to tell you what I felt; this is very important: everybody wakes up every single day with a peace they don't realize they have.

00:09:18.600 --> 00:09:24.021
They go to bed with it and wake up with it.

00:09:25.288 --> 00:09:34.173
Even the worst sinner in the world has a form of peace inside of them that they don't even realize.

00:09:34.787 --> 00:09:53.184
When the rapture happens and we're taken out, there is a void of peace like I've never felt in all of my life; it blankets the earth.

00:09:53.184 --> 00:09:59.580
I used to think that the Holy Spirit left with us because He dwells in each Christian.

00:09:59.580 --> 00:10:07.320
He dwells in us, and when we invite him into our heart, I believe that he went with us when the rapture happened.

00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:10.326
I cannot back that up biblically.

00:10:10.326 --> 00:10:11.428
I don't know.

00:10:11.428 --> 00:10:21.285
All I know is that there is no prayer covering, there is no sense of peace, there is no joy.

00:10:21.710 --> 00:10:25.293
It is absolute chaos.

00:10:25.293 --> 00:10:41.960
And this man has a sense that whenever everybody looks at him, when everybody is gazing upon him, a false sense of peace is what I want to say.

00:10:43.272 --> 00:10:46.373
He brings a peace when he is on the TV.

00:10:46.373 --> 00:10:56.360
He brings a sense of comfort that everybody wants to follow him so quickly because they are so scared and everybody is so tormented.

00:10:56.360 --> 00:11:03.223
They all turn to him so quickly out of that peace that he brings, but it is dirty.

00:11:04.325 --> 00:11:06.996
I don't know how to describe it.

00:11:07.788 --> 00:11:14.849
So he is on the TV, and he is telling everybody what happened to the Christians.

00:11:16.365 --> 00:11:26.788
Then I see people in the Iran and Iraq area over there—Pakistan, that area over there—they were rejoicing.

00:11:26.788 --> 00:11:33.337
And they were all calling out and saying the Mahdi has come.

00:11:33.337 --> 00:11:34.820
The Mahdi has come.

00:11:34.820 --> 00:11:36.944
And I don't know what that means.

00:11:36.944 --> 00:11:41.262
I have studied it now a little bit more.

00:11:42.356 --> 00:11:49.831
I don't know what I'm allowed to say about all this as far as on YouTube and what will be allowed.

00:11:49.831 --> 00:11:55.780
I don't want my video to get flagged, but they were calling it the Mahdi.

00:11:55.780 --> 00:11:58.913
They were calling him the Mahdi.

00:12:00.666 --> 00:12:03.699
And so everybody was calling him the Mahdi.

00:12:09.440 --> 00:12:09.840
And so he was himself Middle Eastern.

00:12:09.840 --> 00:12:12.167
He was a Muslim.

00:12:13.324 --> 00:12:18.506
I know this because he said he was and he had a...

00:12:18.506 --> 00:12:24.400
Okay, I won't get to that part yet.

00:12:24.400 --> 00:12:27.714
Okay, this is what happens next.

00:12:27.714 --> 00:12:37.450
I see him come on TV, and he is telling everybody to bring their Bibles into the stadiums, into these areas.

00:12:46.015 --> 00:12:49.200
He said, 'If you see a Bible, it is mandated by law that everybody brings these Bibles into these areas.

00:12:49.200 --> 00:12:55.160
' And so, it was like courthouses, places like that.

00:12:59.839 --> 00:13:00.049
They were all like police stations, things like that.

00:13:00.049 --> 00:13:03.786
He brings these Bibles in and they start stacking them up—big shelves full.

00:13:03.786 --> 00:13:06.331
There were thousands, millions of Bibles just everywhere.

00:13:06.331 --> 00:13:11.640
And everybody just willfully did it; they just brought in the Bibles.

00:13:12.180 --> 00:13:13.863
And I remember seeing them everywhere.

00:13:13.863 --> 00:13:17.440
There were stacks and stacks of Bibles everywhere.

00:13:18.222 --> 00:13:27.159
And so they would write down your name on a piece of paper of who brought the Bible and what it was or whatever.

00:13:36.427 --> 00:13:36.853
And he told everybody, 'If you want to come and check out the Bible and look at it, it is okay.

00:13:36.853 --> 00:13:40.409
' We'll let you.

00:13:42.079 --> 00:13:59.565
It was kind of a trick, though, because whenever people came in and wrote on the paper to check out their Bible that they brought in—if they wanted to look at it again—you were marked even more so.

00:13:59.565 --> 00:14:04.446
And so it was like you were being watched.

00:14:13.431 --> 00:14:13.707
It was a surveillance state.

00:14:18.080 --> 00:14:18.240
It was really weird.

00:14:18.514 --> 00:14:24.053
It was like a library, is what I want to call it.

00:14:24.053 --> 00:14:37.965
Within a couple of months, I would say I saw a football field with piles of Bibles, probably three or four stories high.

00:14:44.560 --> 00:14:44.880
It was massive—just massive.

00:15:04.880 --> 00:15:05.266
They were all being burned.

00:15:05.653 --> 00:15:09.700
All the Bibles were burned by his order.

00:15:10.999 --> 00:15:12.519
Like I said, the gasoline was all over them.

00:15:12.519 --> 00:15:15.155
They were thrown into the fire, and it was incredible.

00:15:15.155 --> 00:15:23.776
Just massive amounts of smoke and the Bibles all burning.

00:15:23.776 --> 00:15:32.906
Then I saw these flags that he put on every single courthouse.

00:15:32.906 --> 00:15:40.919
If you had a country flag, like the United States of America or Europe, those flags were taken down and his flag was put up.

00:15:40.919 --> 00:16:00.528
It was black, green, and white, and it had these gold swords that were all in the center of it—massive swords, like a saber, is what I want to call it.

00:16:00.528 --> 00:16:12.739
It was a massive sword in the center of this thing, and each color represented a terrorist group, ISIS and others.

00:16:12.739 --> 00:16:34.011
I'm not going to even go there because I don't know all their names, but each was a terrorist group, and they're all being thanked for bringing in his reign because they supported this so much.

00:16:34.011 --> 00:16:42.399
After that, he puts his flag on the buildings, and then this is what happens next.

00:16:42.399 --> 00:16:46.140
I go with Jesus to this other area.

00:16:49.279 --> 00:16:49.760
In this, I see people on Fridays.

00:16:52.150 --> 00:16:54.030
Every Friday, you're required to worship him.

00:16:54.030 --> 00:16:58.480
Every Friday, they all had white outfits on.

00:16:58.480 --> 00:17:10.524
Every person in the world was required to wear a white outfit, and they had white garments on their heads.

00:17:10.524 --> 00:17:12.160
The women did.

00:17:13.759 --> 00:17:16.559
And men had white garments on their heads.

00:17:27.080 --> 00:17:27.340
They had white robes on and they were all in single file lines.

00:17:27.340 --> 00:17:32.000
Every line was perfect and they were all side by side.

00:17:38.183 --> 00:17:38.629
You were required to get on your knees and worship.

00:17:42.159 --> 00:17:46.347
I saw these massive screens—huge screens all on the side of the buildings of these courthouses.

00:17:46.347 --> 00:17:50.018
On Fridays, he would appear wherever you were.

00:17:50.018 --> 00:17:59.900
If it was America or Europe or whatever, you would go to this place of worship on Fridays and look at the screen.

00:17:59.900 --> 00:18:12.896
They would worship him at those screens and it was all over the place, but they were always in white robes.

00:18:12.896 --> 00:18:23.703
They were always in these single lines and it was in town square areas.

00:18:23.703 --> 00:18:32.183
What's really interesting is that I watch a lot of videos on YouTube of people walking tours and stuff.

00:18:32.183 --> 00:18:37.960
There's a place in Rome that I saw that it happens at.

00:18:59.440 --> 00:18:59.773
There are places in my town where I live now.

00:18:59.773 --> 00:19:09.908
There's a place here and there's a place in another town not too far from me where it's being required to worship.

00:19:09.908 --> 00:19:11.576
Very interesting stuff.

00:19:17.140 --> 00:19:17.360
So Christians left.

00:19:17.360 --> 00:19:21.380
Then it goes off of him and I see Christians that were left.

00:19:21.380 --> 00:19:34.854
Now, this is the part that gets hard, and there's probably a lot of you that will disagree with this or get angry about it, but I have to tell you what I saw.

00:19:35.209 --> 00:19:37.327
It is what it is.

00:19:55.832 --> 00:19:56.336
A lot of the grace message that was preached, people lived a compromising lifestyle.

00:19:58.235 --> 00:20:03.119
They were living like the world and they got left.

00:20:03.119 --> 00:20:16.373
There were literally thousands of Christians here that thought they were born again, thought that they were living right, and thought that they did everything right, but they didn't.

00:20:16.373 --> 00:20:21.067
They were living like the world and had an appearance of godliness.

00:20:21.067 --> 00:20:27.600
Their hearts were so far from the Lord, but they thought they were with him.

00:20:27.600 --> 00:20:42.137
They were the ones that even like the Bible talks about: 'You prophesied in my name, you cast out devils in my name, you healed the sick in my name.

00:20:42.137 --> 00:20:44.330
Depart from me; I never knew you.

00:20:44.330 --> 00:20:46.440
' That's what happened.

00:20:46.440 --> 00:20:49.413
There were Christians everywhere.

00:20:49.413 --> 00:21:01.422
There were pastors that I saw who preached that watered-down grace message who were left here in punishment because they were preaching a lukewarm gospel.

00:21:16.960 --> 00:21:17.200
They were left here, and those people were as mad as could be.

00:21:32.087 --> 00:21:32.653
It was terrible.

00:21:32.653 --> 00:21:40.146
They were after those preachers that preached that way.

00:21:40.146 --> 00:21:43.102
They said, "You lied to us.

00:21:43.102 --> 00:21:45.413
You didn't tell us the truth.

00:21:48.996 --> 00:21:49.333
" I was standing with Jesus the whole time.

00:21:49.333 --> 00:21:52.347
He said to me, "Look at this.

00:21:52.347 --> 00:21:53.333
Watch this.

00:21:53.333 --> 00:21:54.320
Remember this.

00:21:54.320 --> 00:21:58.300
" He didn't say it, but I heard his thoughts.

00:21:58.300 --> 00:22:00.876
He said, "Watch this.

00:22:00.876 --> 00:22:02.867
Look at this.

00:22:05.070 --> 00:22:06.135
" I was gazing upon this area.

00:22:06.135 --> 00:22:15.130
I knew after all this happened I was back in time, back before the Antichrist was taking over.

00:22:15.130 --> 00:22:20.366
This is at the beginning, right after the rapture happens.

00:22:30.107 --> 00:22:30.329
The people are mad.

00:22:30.329 --> 00:22:32.578
They are very angry that they're here.

00:22:51.629 --> 00:22:52.424
The pastors and these leaders—I saw some of them, and I'll never mention their names because the Lord told me not to.

00:22:52.424 --> 00:23:06.674
I saw people that were on TV teaching the gospel on TBN and stuff like that—those Christian channels that were actually left.

00:23:06.674 --> 00:23:10.520
Some of them were—like two or three.

00:23:10.520 --> 00:23:19.679
I'm not ever going to say who they were, but I'm going to tell you that they were here.

00:23:19.679 --> 00:23:28.800
There were some folks here, and they were very angry and ready to kill them.

00:23:28.800 --> 00:23:30.080
It was awful.

00:23:35.340 --> 00:23:40.273
I saw one angry Christian lady that I know very well.

00:23:40.273 --> 00:23:46.293
I worked at a church for 13 years; I was a janitor there.

00:23:46.293 --> 00:23:55.920
She was one of the members there at the church where I was.

00:24:11.952 --> 00:24:12.288
I was looking up, and she looked up at the heavens and she flipped the Lord off.

00:24:12.288 --> 00:24:19.200
She gave the Lord the middle finger and she said some expletives, and it was very bad.

00:24:22.746 --> 00:24:23.057
I was watching them all just turn on God.

00:24:23.057 --> 00:24:25.280
They were angry, turning on people.

00:24:25.280 --> 00:24:28.720
There were groups of them that were building colonies.

00:24:28.720 --> 00:24:35.125
They started saying, "We've got to get prepared.

00:24:48.609 --> 00:24:48.919
It's fixing to get really bad.

00:24:48.919 --> 00:24:51.626
We've got to get our stuff around.

00:24:51.626 --> 00:24:53.063
We know what's happened.

00:24:53.063 --> 00:24:54.891
We know what's coming.

00:25:15.813 --> 00:25:16.178
" A lot of them did.

00:25:16.178 --> 00:25:19.554
"We've got to go to the mountains.

00:25:19.554 --> 00:25:23.138
We've got to go to places of refuge.

00:25:23.138 --> 00:25:26.811
We've got to go now because we're running out of time.

00:25:28.251 --> 00:25:31.166
This is fixing to get bad really fast.

00:25:43.760 --> 00:25:43.1000
" I saw these people try to have a camaraderie.

00:25:50.400 --> 00:25:50.800
There were families that were left.

00:26:04.115 --> 00:26:04.610
And this is another thing: everybody below the age of 15 was gone.

00:26:16.740 --> 00:26:16.990
All the little children were gone.

00:26:19.230 --> 00:26:20.550
All of the younger teenagers and pre-teens were gone.

00:26:21.653 --> 00:26:24.388
They all got sucked up in the rapture.

00:26:24.388 --> 00:26:34.960
But anybody that was age of accountability and older was left if you didn't know Jesus Christ and have a relationship with him.

00:26:34.960 --> 00:26:37.937
I watched these younger people go with their families.

00:26:37.937 --> 00:26:40.440
During the tribulation, I saw children being born.

00:26:40.440 --> 00:26:42.133
This part is really hard.

00:26:42.133 --> 00:26:46.026
I watched how the Christians all got together.

00:26:47.750 --> 00:26:52.500
They all go to these mountain areas and dig massive holes in the side of the mountains.

00:26:56.839 --> 00:26:58.177
They were trying to keep warm because you couldn't stay in your house.

00:26:58.177 --> 00:27:04.046
You couldn't go into town and buy groceries because the mark of the beast is coming.

00:27:04.046 --> 00:27:14.690
I'm going to tell you about it; I saw how it happens, how the mark of the beast changes you, and how they put it in your forehead.

00:27:14.690 --> 00:27:23.160
I'll get to that—I don't want to skip around too much or make this too long as I respect people's time.

00:27:35.879 --> 00:27:36.159
The Christians try to move at night.

00:27:36.159 --> 00:27:39.948
I was staying with Jesus, and he took me to a field.

00:27:39.948 --> 00:27:51.075
All I knew was it was dark outside, and the Christians were moving from place to place at night because they couldn't move during the day without being spotted.

00:27:51.626 --> 00:27:54.200
They were trying to get to places of safety.

00:27:54.660 --> 00:27:55.942
The farmers had guns like.

00:27:55.942 --> 00:28:05.010
22s and rifles, so there were still firearms and ways of protection for farmers, but I didn't see many other people with guns.

00:28:18.920 --> 00:28:19.227
The Christians didn't have guns.

00:28:19.227 --> 00:28:27.229
I don't know why—nothing was really said about that—but I know the farmers did.

00:28:27.229 --> 00:28:42.479
I remember seeing one place where these Christians were trying to go through a pasture, and dogs barking alerted the farmer inside the house.

00:28:50.640 --> 00:28:50.880
He flipped the light on, and he had a.

00:28:50.880 --> 00:28:53.620
22 in his hand.

00:28:53.620 --> 00:28:57.662
I know it was a.

00:28:57.662 --> 00:28:58.851
22.

00:29:07.400 --> 00:29:07.980
He fired it and called the authorities to tell them people were moving at night.

00:29:20.640 --> 00:29:20.870
He didn't know if they were Christians, but I knew they were.

00:29:20.870 --> 00:29:27.699
Then I saw men in black armored Hummer trucks with blue, infrared-looking lights inside the back.

00:29:46.399 --> 00:29:46.826
They were all black with blacked-out windows.

00:29:46.826 --> 00:30:02.1000
As they drove, the Christians tried to put cement blocks in the road to slow them down so they would have enough time to run away as fast as they could.

00:30:02.1000 --> 00:30:14.760
They would try to throw things in the road to slow their approach, and they were running as fast as they could to try to get away.

00:30:14.760 --> 00:30:23.071
These men had black face masks on, like COVID masks, and black hoods, and they would jump out.

00:30:26.725 --> 00:30:34.791
They had black outfits on with these vests and would jump out of these black cars with these guns.

00:30:34.791 --> 00:30:40.240
But this is what's weird: I've never seen one of these before.

00:30:40.240 --> 00:30:46.099
I've tried to find them online and I can't; I've never seen this before.

00:30:46.099 --> 00:30:48.559
It was a pulse.

00:30:52.833 --> 00:30:58.685
They took these black guns and pointed them and shot, but it wasn't a bullet.

00:30:58.685 --> 00:31:13.658
It was electric, like an electromagnetic pulse, and it just stuns you, but it didn't have any stun to it like the cords that come out like they have now.

00:31:18.952 --> 00:31:23.790
It was some kind of wave of energy that came out of these things and knocked you senseless for a couple of seconds.

00:31:23.790 --> 00:31:32.160
They didn't have to reload it; they just pointed it, and the people running fell out on the ground.

00:31:34.040 --> 00:31:45.644
They would pass out right there, and by the time they would get up, it was too late; they were held captive.

00:31:45.644 --> 00:31:48.329
These men would give them an ultimatum.

00:32:00.377 --> 00:32:00.794
I saw a woman and she had these two young children—a boy and a girl born during the Tribulation.

00:32:00.794 --> 00:32:05.840
They were probably three or four years old, maybe more.

00:32:05.840 --> 00:32:10.411
They were talking, so they were young, maybe five.

00:32:10.411 --> 00:32:22.319
They said, 'We're going to give the children the chip first, and if you don't deny your Jesus, we're going to cut your kids' heads off.

00:32:22.319 --> 00:32:25.406
We're going to cut their heads off.

00:32:25.406 --> 00:32:28.106
' Or you could take the chip.

00:32:28.106 --> 00:32:30.199
They gave them an ultimatum.

00:32:30.199 --> 00:32:33.300
The dad said, 'No, we're not taking the mark.

00:32:33.300 --> 00:32:34.619
We will die.

00:32:34.619 --> 00:32:38.103
' The dad said, 'We're most certainly not taking the mark.

00:32:38.103 --> 00:32:43.074
' The mother said, 'No, you can't cut my babies' heads off!

00:32:43.074 --> 00:32:49.457
' because the man had this huge sickle, a huge sword, in his hand.

00:32:49.457 --> 00:33:02.329
He was getting ready—he had the baby's head like this—and he was getting ready to just go and slice that kid's head off right there.

00:33:09.679 --> 00:33:10.179
There was no mercy.

00:33:10.179 --> 00:33:14.148
There was no conscience about it.

00:33:14.148 --> 00:33:17.890
It was just the way it was.

00:33:26.589 --> 00:33:26.899
And the dad cried out and said, "No, you must not take the mark.

00:33:31.140 --> 00:33:37.073
" And when he said that, they cut his head off right there.

00:33:41.067 --> 00:33:44.460
And I'm talking it fell and rolled at my feet, and I could smell his blood.

00:33:44.460 --> 00:33:47.257
That's how awful it was.

00:33:47.257 --> 00:33:53.640
Jesus stood there with me the whole time, and he never made a comment about it.

00:33:53.640 --> 00:33:56.069
He just told me to look.

00:34:03.787 --> 00:34:04.191
And so I looked and I watched the woman, and she said, "I'll take the mark.

00:34:04.191 --> 00:34:04.596
I'll take it.

00:34:04.596 --> 00:34:07.256
I'll take the chip.

00:34:07.256 --> 00:34:09.560
Don't take their heads.

00:34:13.093 --> 00:34:15.515
" And this is what is so incredible; it's absolutely amazing about this part.

00:34:29.484 --> 00:34:29.889
They take this chip, and instantaneously those children were crying because they just saw their dad die right in front of them.

00:34:35.942 --> 00:34:40.560
And the mom is crying and she's bawling her eyes out because she saw her husband die right in front of her.

00:34:44.120 --> 00:34:47.319
And the moment she takes the chip, the baby, the two children, and her instantaneously lose emotion.

00:34:52.799 --> 00:34:53.199
They don't have any emotion on their face.

00:34:54.619 --> 00:34:55.640
They totally lose the crying.

00:34:55.640 --> 00:35:02.780
It's like they went like a zombie right there in front of me.

00:35:02.780 --> 00:35:05.769
Their minds and everything had a peace again.

00:35:05.769 --> 00:35:09.540
It's like the chip sent a peace to their brain somehow.

00:35:20.960 --> 00:35:21.360
I don't know how; all I know is the chip did something to them and it made them calm.

00:35:26.060 --> 00:35:27.147
It put off some kind of endorphin in them, and they just went cold in their face, like they're not there.

00:35:27.147 --> 00:35:32.259
It's like, "Hello, you're not there," and they were not crying about him anymore.

00:35:45.520 --> 00:35:45.920
It's like they didn't care.

00:35:57.1000 --> 00:35:58.560
And so I saw that, and then I saw a man trying to commit suicide, and he already had the mark.

00:35:58.560 --> 00:36:12.650
He had the chip in his hand, and he was standing on a major bridge, and all of a sudden the chip sent a signal to his brain and calmed him down and he did not kill himself.

00:36:22.309 --> 00:36:22.659
I don't understand why; I don't understand how.

00:36:22.659 --> 00:36:36.320
All I know is that chip produced some kind of signal, some kind of endorphin somehow, and calmed his mind down, and instantaneously he became calm and he did not jump off that bridge.

00:36:38.900 --> 00:36:45.794
It knew; I don't know how it knew that you were fixing to do something like that.

00:36:45.794 --> 00:36:55.360
Then I would see people mowing their grass and I would walk by them, but they couldn't see me.

00:36:55.680 --> 00:37:03.188
I would walk by them and they were mowing, but they were not there.

00:37:03.188 --> 00:37:16.606
It's like you could go, "Hello," but you were just in another world, way out there, like a zombie.

00:37:16.606 --> 00:37:18.869
It was weird.

00:37:26.260 --> 00:37:31.119
They were just mowing their grass like robots, but the chip would bring something to their biological brain.

00:37:31.119 --> 00:37:34.368
I don't get it.

00:37:34.368 --> 00:37:43.530
Another thing I thought was interesting is that I watched them.

00:37:43.530 --> 00:37:53.184
Jesus took me to a place in a town, and there were these barricades all over, massive gray barricades, huge.

00:37:57.520 --> 00:37:57.794
There were men with armed guards and guns all around.

00:37:58.891 --> 00:38:10.090
You would have to go through these barricades to get into these towns; you had to have your chip in your hand.

00:38:10.090 --> 00:38:20.011
If you didn't have the chip, you couldn't get in, and they would offer you the chip or you would die.

00:38:36.540 --> 00:38:36.920
They would kill you right there—no questions.

00:38:43.215 --> 00:38:43.527
If you didn't take it, they'd cut your head off.

00:38:54.507 --> 00:38:54.800
There was a woman—I remember her face.

00:38:54.800 --> 00:38:59.920
She was a white woman with brown hair, and she was standing in line.

00:39:01.200 --> 00:39:06.480
A lot of people, though not everyone, had a bruise on their head; it was a burn sore.

00:39:09.333 --> 00:39:11.929
The body had a reaction to the chip and it caused sores on people's heads.

00:39:11.929 --> 00:39:17.966
It was like burn sores, and there were burn sores on their hands—not everyone, though.

00:39:17.966 --> 00:39:29.114
She was trying to mimic it with makeup, trying to put makeup on her hand to make it look like she had a burn sore.

00:39:29.114 --> 00:39:41.800
She was standing in line, and when she got up to go in through the gate, they saw that she was trying to fake it.

00:39:41.800 --> 00:39:55.080
People were so desperate for food and for whatever resources they could get into the towns that they were willing to do whatever it took.

00:39:55.080 --> 00:39:57.100
She was a Christian, basically.

00:39:57.100 --> 00:40:05.749
I guess I don't know who she really was; the moment they saw her faking it, they cut her head off right there.

00:40:05.749 --> 00:40:09.257
There was no time for even repentance.

00:40:12.411 --> 00:40:16.560
They just took a sickle-sword and cut her head off like it was nothing.

00:40:16.560 --> 00:40:21.710
Her head rolled out, and people in line who were watching acted like it was nothing.

00:40:21.710 --> 00:40:22.850
There was no emotion.

00:40:22.850 --> 00:40:28.449
I'm telling you, there was no emotion to these people; they were gone.

00:40:28.449 --> 00:40:29.190
It was weird.

00:40:29.190 --> 00:40:36.800
I'm just telling you what I saw and I'm trying to figure it out myself.

00:40:36.800 --> 00:40:43.938
I'm still trying to figure out the nanotechnology.

00:41:02.1000 --> 00:41:04.119
And the only thing that I think is really close to this nanotechnology is what a very rich man here in America is working on—I don't want to say his name.

00:41:04.119 --> 00:41:13.725
If you go and look at it, he's working on chips right now on pigs.

00:41:13.725 --> 00:41:17.960
That's all I can say.

00:41:35.940 --> 00:41:36.670
And it's very similar.

00:41:51.360 --> 00:41:51.560
But this chip goes—it's very small, like a very small square.

00:42:07.919 --> 00:42:08.320
I don't know how it gets power, if it gets it from your body's energy.

00:42:08.320 --> 00:42:11.982
I don't know, because it didn't have a battery.

00:42:11.982 --> 00:42:15.640
There's no way a battery could be that small.

00:42:15.640 --> 00:42:33.270
Like I said, these men carried around these guns that were like waves of energy and they knocked you down.

00:42:48.811 --> 00:42:49.474
It's like super sci-fi, but it's not.

00:42:49.474 --> 00:42:53.543
It's legit what I saw.

00:42:53.543 --> 00:43:00.746
Then I saw the Christians again, and this is part of it.

00:43:00.746 --> 00:43:11.120
I'm praying I'm not skipping around too much, because I'm telling you how I remember it.

00:43:11.120 --> 00:43:14.231
They were digging these foxholes.

00:43:16.009 --> 00:43:16.720
And the winters were terrible.

00:43:23.640 --> 00:43:23.990
The further north they went in the mountains, the colder the temperatures were.

00:43:29.500 --> 00:43:31.280
I don't know what kind of catastrophic events of nature happened there, because I didn't see that.

00:43:31.920 --> 00:43:37.064
All I know is that the winters were awful, and people died from starvation and the cold quickly.

00:43:37.064 --> 00:43:38.440
It was bad.

00:43:38.440 --> 00:43:47.626
Here comes another part: I look up in the sky because I hear these noises, and there are thousands of drones.

00:43:47.626 --> 00:43:48.462
Thousands.

00:43:48.462 --> 00:43:49.640
No joke.

00:43:49.640 --> 00:43:50.400
Thousands.

00:43:50.780 --> 00:43:59.470
They are all in sequence with each other, flying across the sky, scanning the horizon and scanning everybody.

00:43:59.470 --> 00:44:09.920
The chip in your hand or your forehead would report back to these drones that you had it.

00:44:09.920 --> 00:44:16.631
These drones would fly throughout the woods, throughout all areas, the oceans, everywhere.

00:44:16.631 --> 00:44:22.200
They were flying throughout all of America, all over the place.

00:44:35.770 --> 00:44:36.215
You could literally hear them coming, and they could sense your body heat, your motion, and everything.

00:44:36.215 --> 00:44:41.234
So, you couldn't hide from them.

00:45:03.105 --> 00:45:03.590
The only way I saw that the Christians could hide from them was digging into the side of the hills.

00:45:05.965 --> 00:45:08.456
The drones were looking for smoke or gunshots.

00:45:08.456 --> 00:45:22.750
So the Christians couldn't shoot for food—rabbits or deer or anything that made noise—because the drones in the sky could hear the noises.

00:45:22.760 --> 00:45:31.140
They were alerted and would swarm to that area and see who did it.

00:45:31.140 --> 00:45:42.747
If you had the chip, it would report back and they would just go on about their business.

00:45:42.747 --> 00:45:59.333
But if you didn't have the chip, they would call for the authorities, who would come and stay there until they arrived.

00:46:02.640 --> 00:46:03.060
You would run, but you couldn't get away.

00:46:05.580 --> 00:46:09.760
You couldn't get away from them because they were up like a helicopter.

00:46:20.057 --> 00:46:20.354
They were flying over, and once they found you, you were done.

00:46:34.183 --> 00:46:34.491
They would come and either you took the chip or you took the mark, or they cut your head off.

00:46:34.491 --> 00:46:53.806
These Christians were all on the side of mountains—people that were still fighting to live and survive, who were not living for Jesus when they were on the earth, but they knew the truth.

00:47:05.599 --> 00:47:05.885
They knew.

00:47:05.885 --> 00:47:10.600
The children were the hardest part for me, those born during the Tribulation.

00:47:22.759 --> 00:47:23.400
I know there's a Bible verse that says, 'Woe to those that give suck in those days.

00:47:23.400 --> 00:47:35.627
' I believe that verse is talking about the Tribulation, but all I know is that the kids were taking it really hard.

00:47:35.627 --> 00:47:42.600
They were going inside, and the smoke was coming out of these caves.

00:47:42.600 --> 00:47:47.502
They were trying to keep the fires really low so that the drones couldn't see it.

00:48:01.173 --> 00:48:01.457
The drones would fly throughout the earth, and they sounded like swarms of bees beyond anything.

00:48:13.930 --> 00:48:14.220
It was incredibly loud.

00:48:14.220 --> 00:48:22.640
Swarms of bees were everywhere, and you knew when they were coming because you could hear them from a distance.

00:48:22.640 --> 00:48:38.295
Everybody would scramble, trying to get into their safe zone as fast as they could to try to hide themselves.

00:48:38.295 --> 00:48:42.551
They were made to worship on Fridays.

00:48:42.551 --> 00:48:49.982
I told you about the people and the mark of the beast; they had the Abomination of Desolation chip in their hands.

00:48:49.982 --> 00:48:53.337
Now I want to tell you about the Abomination of Desolation.

00:48:59.148 --> 00:49:02.359
I was all of a sudden translated to Israel, and I see this great big temple.

00:49:02.359 --> 00:49:13.257
It's on a hill, elevated, with these massive stone columns all inside of it and a roof.

00:49:19.155 --> 00:49:20.808
There is a place where people can come at the base of this temple.

00:49:20.808 --> 00:49:27.200
I'm standing at the base of the temple with Jesus, looking up.

00:49:35.480 --> 00:49:36.000
The temple is elevated, and the Antichrist has a podium.

00:49:36.000 --> 00:49:45.326
He's standing in between those big columns with a man on either side of him.

00:49:45.326 --> 00:49:51.217
I don't know who this man is right here on his other hand.

00:50:09.920 --> 00:50:10.160
I believe he's another form of a religion.

00:50:10.160 --> 00:50:14.720
I'm not familiar with a lot of other leaders and other religious beliefs.

00:50:14.720 --> 00:50:22.755
I'll say that he had olive skin, lightning bolts, and darker hair also.

00:50:22.755 --> 00:50:28.423
But that's all I'm going to say about that.

00:50:28.423 --> 00:50:39.040
So, I'm looking up and there are lightning bolts shooting all over the sky.

00:50:39.040 --> 00:50:45.223
I'm talking—it's like total chaos, lightning—but none of it's touching the ground.

00:50:45.223 --> 00:50:48.240
It's just going all over the sky.

00:50:48.240 --> 00:50:55.661
And the Lord won't let me see his eyes from here, around all this.

00:51:03.760 --> 00:51:04.140
But I see the Antichrist again, and he's standing there proclaiming that he is God on the Temple Mount.

00:51:08.514 --> 00:51:16.506
And he has at this time—not every time that I see him, like when he was at the beginning when he first appears in Berlin—he didn't have a beard.

00:51:16.506 --> 00:51:26.319
I didn't see his eyes there, but I saw that he had olive skin and he was clean-cut and clean-shaven at this time.

00:51:26.319 --> 00:51:28.180
I don't know why.

00:51:42.933 --> 00:51:43.200
But at this time, he has a beard and it's salt and pepper—like black and white—a beard, and the sides of his hair were black and white.

00:51:43.200 --> 00:51:46.622
They were not strictly white or strictly black.

00:51:46.622 --> 00:51:51.440
He had spots of gray coming through his hair similar to mine.

00:51:54.745 --> 00:51:56.094
But he had hair; he wasn't bald.

00:51:56.094 --> 00:52:10.257
He had a white turban hat on, like a rag-type garment on his head.

00:52:23.680 --> 00:52:24.320
I could see that—like I said, I couldn't see his eyes—but he had some kind of glasses on.

00:52:24.320 --> 00:52:38.329
He was about 5'11" to 6 feet tall from what I could see while looking up like this because it's in person now.

00:52:38.329 --> 00:52:42.440
He was probably around 195 to 215 pounds in weight.

00:52:42.440 --> 00:52:48.700
I'll describe him like this: he carries himself like a James Bond.

00:53:05.969 --> 00:53:06.544
It may sound dumb, but I'm just going to say it like this.

00:53:06.544 --> 00:53:25.179
He carries himself very confidently, very poised in the way he talked, similar to the way Barack Obama used to whenever he delivered his speeches to the State of the Union.

00:53:25.729 --> 00:53:34.680
The way he carried himself, he spoke very intelligently; he was very poised and very precise.

00:53:34.680 --> 00:53:43.820
He had a way to draw you in; he made you like him.

00:53:48.411 --> 00:53:49.783
It was so peaceful, and the way he communicated to you just brought peace.

00:53:49.783 --> 00:53:57.320
It was really weird, very strange because everybody was just fixated on his face.

00:53:57.320 --> 00:54:08.446
He brought the peace they used to feel, the peace I told you about at the beginning that you didn't feel anymore.

00:54:26.731 --> 00:54:27.097
He brought that peace you didn't feel.

00:54:46.933 --> 00:54:47.387
He brought that sense of comfort that I said every person wakes up with every single day and goes to bed with as a sinner; they don't even realize it.

00:54:47.840 --> 00:54:49.200
And that's peace.

00:54:49.200 --> 00:55:00.889
It's like a prayer covering that the body of Christ brings into this world, and we probably don't even realize that we bring it.

00:55:03.909 --> 00:55:16.977
The church doesn't even realize the power they have, the atmosphere we create with our prayers, the atmosphere we create every day.

00:55:33.120 --> 00:55:33.419
And then when we're gone, it's hell on earth.

00:55:33.419 --> 00:55:34.319
It's awful.

00:55:37.497 --> 00:55:43.714
And for the first time, why he is so attractive is when he speaks, nobody else feels that anymore.

00:55:53.280 --> 00:55:53.520
But he has a falseness, a false peace that everybody pursues and wants.

00:55:53.520 --> 00:56:01.839
Again, they're starving for it; they don't have it, and so they're looking for it.

00:56:02.102 --> 00:56:08.071
And he has a dirtiness; it's a dirty falseness that they're all wanting, they're all looking for again.

00:56:08.071 --> 00:56:10.920
And so he sucks you in.

00:56:10.920 --> 00:56:17.291
At this time, during this part of the visitation, I'm taken out of the earth.

00:56:17.291 --> 00:56:27.396
I'm sucked up out of the earth and I go to the edge of heaven and earth, and I'm standing there.

00:56:27.396 --> 00:56:31.333
I can turn around and I can look and I see the gates of heaven.

00:56:37.591 --> 00:56:39.484
I see the holy city is beautiful all behind me, and Jesus is standing right here this time on my left.

00:56:46.960 --> 00:56:49.399
And he speaks to me this time and he says, 'Look at the earth; I want to show you something that's about to take place.

00:56:49.399 --> 00:56:53.987
' And I said, 'You know, I'm just excited.

00:56:53.987 --> 00:57:02.628
' I look over and I look at the earth and it's spinning; I can see it moving.

00:57:14.471 --> 00:57:14.747
And he said, 'Do you see each one of those lights down there?

00:57:14.747 --> 00:57:16.865
' And I said, 'Yeah.

00:57:16.865 --> 00:57:20.775
' He goes, 'Those represent souls.

00:57:20.775 --> 00:57:36.844
' And he said there is going to be a major revival about to happen throughout the earth—a final push, a final harvest, a China major harvest.

00:57:36.844 --> 00:57:49.491
It's like—and I don't want to add any words that he didn't say, but that's what he showed me.

00:58:09.799 --> 00:58:10.279
And then he started—I look over at him, I'm looking over, and I look at his eyes and they're welled up with tears.

00:58:10.279 --> 00:58:14.615
He said, 'Do you see China?

00:58:14.615 --> 00:58:18.826
' And I said, 'Yeah.

00:58:18.826 --> 00:58:27.440
' He said, 'They, a lot of them, died for my gospel.

00:58:27.440 --> 00:58:31.360
' "The gospel cost them something, Brandon.

00:58:31.360 --> 00:58:41.805
" He looked at him and was so filled with joy at the sacrifice they gave for the gospel.

00:58:41.805 --> 00:58:49.094
What I saw when I was looking over were these gold streams.

00:58:50.426 --> 00:59:00.285
They were like gold streets, but they weren't, because I knew each one of those lights represented a soul.

00:59:07.030 --> 00:59:07.448
I said, "Lord, what is that?

00:59:15.453 --> 00:59:15.867
" He said, "That's the underground churches in China.

00:59:32.559 --> 00:59:32.845
" He said, "Each one of those represents a soul.

00:59:36.319 --> 00:59:43.359
" It's just amazing because I'm looking at the Asian souls that get saved and they spread all throughout Asia.

01:00:04.262 --> 01:00:04.537
You can see these gold veins that go up through North Korea, South Korea, and Japan.

01:00:04.537 --> 01:00:10.920
Then I looked over at the Philippines and there were lights in the Philippines.

01:00:10.920 --> 01:00:26.786
